description.narrative: UNICEF Gambia Country Office (GCO) continued to promote preventive and response services with partners, including through the decentralized structures, for vulnerable children (including children on the move) to address their needs and the challenges they face in their daily lives. GCO and partners established the Children's National Assembly and actively supported youth engagement and participation activities within community and regional structures including the use of the U report platform for children. Additionally, GCO supported the NGO partners and MWCSW on FGM and child marriage elimination. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:27/12/2019
